Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.43,0:18:36.43,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}｢写真撮ろー！｣
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.43,0:18:37.64,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}てか　Why don't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.64,0:18:40.10,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}何か始まっちゃう予感
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.68,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}ただライクに混沌
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.65,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}なんかその　わかってくれそうだと思った
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.65,0:18:45.61,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}間違ってた？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.61,0:18:48.07,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}あなたこそが僕の生活
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.07,0:18:49.65,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}故に　I need you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.69,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}君の性格　無自覚？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.69,0:18:52.90,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}伝わるテレパス
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.37,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}この友情って一生ものかも
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.37,0:18:57.24,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}なによりもラブ=愛なの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.24,0:18:57.99,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}全力
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.62,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}つまり　I love you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.87,ED-JP-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(20,20)}更に　I need you
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,ED-CN-1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.80,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}原來我們喜歡的東西一模一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:04.06,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}我跟那種閃閃發光的生活根本不沾邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.52,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}但有你在的話  再困難我也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.40,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}雖然會有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.07,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.16,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}好多事都想不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:14.32,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}我們當初是怎麼開始的來著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.66,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}算了  那種事也無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:18.75,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}啊  心跳得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:21.96,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}絕望可是種奢侈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.96,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}可不能浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.54,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}給這平淡無奇的日子將上一軍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:29.67,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}只要和我一起  說不定你也能改變世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.68,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}記憶也好  妄想也罷  全都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:35.43,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}我等友情乃是永久不滅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:36.43,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}“來拍照吧!”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:37.64,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}話說  Why don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:40.10,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}總感覺要有什麼事情發生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.68,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}即使好感中夾雜著混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.65,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}但感覺你好像能夠理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:45.61,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}是我搞錯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:48.07,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}你就是我生活的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:49.65,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}因此 I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.69,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}你的性格  自己都沒意識到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:52.90,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}我們就是心有靈犀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.37,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}這份友情也許是一輩子的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:57.24,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}不管怎樣  Love就是愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:57.99,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}拚盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.62,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}也就是說  I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.87,ED-CN-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(20,70)}更加  I need you
